posting_body: ['At Foxborough Apartments, we have taken every measure to ensure that your home will be impeccable.', 'From custom designed interiors that have been updated, to the natural beauty of the well maintained grounds and exteriors; we strive to provide the perfect setting for wonderful times and fond memories.', 'Relax at one of our pools that are lined with beautiful gazebos, get fit in our fitness center, access the internet in our new business center, and check out a movie from our recent releases selection.', 'Our professional staff is here for you, to provide prompt, courteous attention to your needs and a comfortable style of living.', '-Cable Ready', '-15 Mins.', 'from the New Cowboys Stadium & Baseball Park', '-Gazebo sundeck', '-2012, 2013, 2014, 2015, 2017, 2019  Apartment Ratings - Top Rated Award Recipient', '-Minutes from DFW Airport', '-Monthly Resident Events', '-Upgraded Packages with new black appliances', '-High Vaulted Ceilings', '-Disposal', '-Spanish Speaking Staff', '-24 hour Fitness Center', '-Clubhouse', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
